title: Mad Games Tycoon v0.150405A
description:
Update: 0.150405A

- 12 new objects added.
- Added new speed level.
- You can now see the revenues from engines.
- If you are researching something, you now get XP.
- Randomization of Platform Popularity as a new game toggle-able option.
- Now in the archived game concepts, graphics, sound, technology and gameplay points are displayed.
- Now you can disable "post-process effects" in the options.
- Added Hungarian language.
- Different languages have been updated.
- Bug removed: With some graphics cards, the screen was flipped.
- Various minor bugs fixed
